  "title": "Rich Velvety Japanese Cranberry Ochazuke",
  "description": "A tangy and velvety Japanese dish featuring cranberry juice and ferment-kimchi, perfect for a comforting meal. This vegetarian-friendly recipe is a nostalgic twist on traditional ochazuke.",
